OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FVictims of crime are facing an
OL,7,F"unacceptable wait" for justice, as
OL,8,Fthe backlog of cases waiting to be
OL,9,Fheard at crown courts in England and
OL,10,FWales has risen to a record level.
OL,12,FNearly 80,000 cases remained open at
OL,13,Fthe end of June 2025, according to
OL,14,FMinistry of Justice figures released
OL,15,Fon Thursday.
OL,17,FThe latest figure of 78,329 open cases
OL,18,Fis up 2% compared to the end of March,
OL,19,Fwhen the backlog surpassed 75,000 for
OL,20,Fthe first time.
