OL,6,FThe number of open cases was also up
OL,7,F10% from 70,893 a year earlier,
OL,8,Faccording to the figures.
OL,10,FSome 19,164 cases had been open for at
OL,11,Fleast a year at the end of June, up
OL,12,F17% from 16,378 a year earlier and the
OL,13,Fhighest since current data began.
