OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FEarlier this month a crown court judge
OL,7,Fhit out at the "chronic" backlog of
OL,8,Fcases after TV presenter Jay Blades
OL,9,Fwas told he will not face trial for
OL,10,Ftwo years.
OL,12,FSpeaking at Shrewsbury Crown Court,
OL,13,FJudge Anthony Lowe said "it is not a
OL,14,Fproper justice system where people are
OL,15,Fhaving to wait that length of time for
OL,16,Ftheir trial", as he adjourned the 55-
OL,17,Fyear-old's rape case until September
OL,18,F2027.
