OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister and Justice
OL,7,FSecretary David Lammy said the backlog
OL,8,F"lays bare the unacceptable wait
OL,9,Fvictims face".
OL,11,F"Money alone cannot turn the tide on
OL,12,Fthe rising backlog which is why we
OL,13,Fasked Sir Brian Leveson to propose
OL,14,Fbold and ambitious reform, to put our
OL,15,Fjustice system back on sustainable
OL,16,Fground."
