OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FMinisters are set to respond this
OL,7,Fautumn to recommendations made by Sir
OL,8,FBrian to overhaul the courts system
OL,9,Fand tackle the backlog, where some
OL,10,Fcases are listed for 2029.
OL,12,FThe major review, published in July,
OL,13,Fproposed reducing the number of jury
OL,14,Ftrials and create a new type of crown
OL,15,Fcourt where trials are heard by judges.
OL,17,FThe review commissioned by the
OL,18,Fgovernment is aimed at trying to
OL,19,F"reduce the risk of total system
OL,20,Fcollapse".
