OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FNearly a third of the crown court
OL,7,Fbacklog at the end of June was cases
OL,8,Finvolving violence against the person
OL,9,F(31%), with around one in six being
OL,10,Fsexual offences (17%) and around one
OL,11,Fin seven drug offences (14%).
OL,13,FThese three categories of offence
OL,14,Ftogether accounted for nearly two-
OL,15,Fthirds (62%) of the full backlog.
OL,17,FThere were a record 4,086 rape cases
OL,18,Fin the crown court backlog as of the
OL,19,Fend of June, up 31% year on year from
OL,20,F3,114.
