OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FReacting to the latest figures,
OL,7,Fchairwoman of the Criminal Bar
OL,8,FAssociation Riel Karmy-Jones KC said
OL,9,Fthat on Thursday a case was listed for
OL,10,Ftrial in October 2029 at Isleworth
OL,11,FCrown Court.
OL,13,F"Criminal barristers who prosecute and
OL,14,Fdefend cases involving the very
OL,15,Fvulnerable have been working to keep
OL,16,Fthis crumbling system from collapsing
OL,17,Ffor years ` but it has become
OL,18,Funsustainable," she said.
