OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FManchester Arena bomb plotter Hashem
OL,7,FAbedi was among those due to appear at
OL,8,Fthe court charged with attempting to
OL,9,Fmurder prison officers, but court
OL,10,Fofficials said there was no water in
OL,11,Fthe building and that it was a public
OL,12,Fhealth risk.
OL,14,FThere is also a new record backlog in
OL,15,Fmagistrates' courts of 361,027 cases,
OL,16,Fup 25% on 289,595 a year earlier.
