OL,3,CVictims face 'unacceptable wait' as
OL,4,Ccrown court backlog hits record level
OL,6,FThe rise comes as magistrates were
OL,7,Fgiven more sentencing powers in
OL,8,FOctober last year, allowing them to
OL,9,Fhear cases that carry a maximum prison
OL,10,Fsentence of up to 12 months, up from
OL,11,Fsix months previously.
OL,13,FThe move aimed to free up crown court
OL,14,Ftime to deal with the most serious
OL,15,Fcases and cut the backlog while also
OL,16,Fseeking to better-support victims.
